snippet.title: Spectrobes: Origins E3 trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.facebook.com/spectrobesgame

A first look at Spectrobes: Origins, the new Action Adventure game from Disney Interactive Studios that features a blazingly fast real-time combat system, all new 3D fossil excavations, and 2 player drop in, drop out co-op play.

http://www.spectrobesorigins.com
